Sentencas: A new type of a high temperature liquid metal-air energy storage cell based on solid oxide electrolyte has been successfully demonstrated at 750 degrees C by feeding metal Sn.
Titulo: High-temperature liquid Sn-air energy storage cell

Sentencas: In order to understanding the initial size effect of metal as a liquid fuel, we report here the impact of the thermal and electrochemical oxidation behavior of nano Sn (similar to 100 nm), comparing with micro-sized (similar to 5 mu m) and macro-sized (similar to 350 mu m) Sn.
Titulo: High-temperature liquid Sn-air energy storage cell

Sentencas: The thermogravimetric analysis and the monitoring OCV test indicate that the distinct property of nano-sized Sn results in a favorable thermal oxidation behavior near the melting point and a promising power performance due to enhanced fuel transport to the anode.
Titulo: High-temperature liquid Sn-air energy storage cell

Titulo: High-temperature liquid Sn-air energy storage cell
